      Subclasses of Channel in org.vngx.jsch 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  ChannelDirectTCPIP
      Implementation of Channel for client-to-server forwarded connections over TCP/IP.
      class  ChannelExec
      Implementation of ChannelSession which allows for the execution of a single command at a time and pipes the output from command to a stream.
      class  ChannelForwardedTCPIP
      Implementation of Channel for server-to-client forwarded connections over TCP/IP.
      class  ChannelSftp
      Implementation of ChannelSession for opening a SFTP channel which runs as a subsystem for "sftp".
      class  ChannelShell
      Implementation of ChannelSession which can be used for creating a shell to allow input and output streams for communicating over SSH.
